<feed xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><id>https://www.discuss.com.hk/forumdisplay.php?fid=57&amp;orderby=dateline&amp;ascdesc=DESC&amp;filter=0</id><title>HKDiscuss money</title><updated>2025-07-28T02:30:06.631437+00:00</updated><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/forumdisplay.php?fid=57&amp;orderby=dateline&amp;ascdesc=DESC&amp;filter=0"/><generator uri="https://lkiesow.github.io/python-feedgen" version="1.0.0">python-feedgen</generator><subtitle>Latest articles</subtitle><entry><id>0723ff8d8b7c16c8e521394a8e7af346</id><title>金價衝高需ETF資金重燃 大行點出關鍵催化劑 明年目標4000美元</title><updated>2025-07-27T21:42:17+08:00</updated><author><name>258仔仔</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-07-27T21:42:17+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_573382159"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_573382159"&gt;&lt;span id="attach_16394088" onmouseover="showMenu(this.id, 0, 1)" style="position: absolute; display: none"&gt;&lt;img border="0" src="images/discuss_style/attachimg.gif"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;div class="post-img-container" data-pid="573382159" original-img="https://img.discuss.com.hk/attachments/day_250727/20250727_de61e91cee8e1e90b927euY3x2jBGzwg.png"&gt;&lt;img border="0" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/9261b9/f/800x0/https://img.discuss.com.hk/attachments/day_250727/20250727_de61e91cee8e1e90b927euY3x2jBGzwg.png"/&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="t_attach" id="attach_16394088_menu" style="position: absolute; display: none"&gt;&lt;img alt="" border="0" class="absmiddle" src="images/attachicons/image.gif"&gt; &lt;a href="attachment.php?aid=16394088&amp;amp;nothumb=yes" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;image.png&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt; (692.08 KB)&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="t_smallfont"&gt;2025-7-27 21:42&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;br/&gt;美國早前與日本達成貿易協議後，市場憧憬歐美也可以很快達成協議，令市場避險情緒降溫，現貨金價自上周三起連跌3日，周五收報3,337美元，按周跌0.4%；不過，有大行認為，金價長期結構性利好因素仍然存在，下一個催化劑可能是美國就業數據惡化，從而令聯儲局兌現減息預期，甚至預計明年初達到4,000美元。值得留意的是，雖然市場幾乎一面倒預期美國聯儲局本周四（31日）公佈的議息結果將按兵不動，但美國本周仍將接連公佈GDP、就業報告及核心通脹指標，一系列事件及數據或將重塑減息及金價前景。&lt;br/&gt;美就業惡化料成最大催化劑&lt;br/&gt;據內媒引述摩根大通最新報告指出，未來金價衝高關鍵在於能否重燃ETF的資金流入，但這需要聯儲局兌現減息預期及推動美國實際收益率下行，其中美國就業數據惡化將可能是最大催化劑。&lt;br/&gt;該行表示，央行持續購金為金價提供了支撐，而ETF資金流入則是金價上漲的關鍵動力，並預測今年全球黃金ETF持有量將淨增加715噸。若以年初至今計，全球ETF持有量增加了407噸，完成了預期的一半多一點，其中美國約203噸、中國約86噸，其他地區亦有118噸；雖然中國ETF流入的相對穩定令人鼓舞，但整體ETF流入量缺乏了今年稍早的強度。&lt;br/&gt;ETF資金對實際利率敏感&lt;br/&gt;該行又指，ETF資金是否流入對實際利率敏感，特別是在大規模月度ETF流入方面。自2010年以來，全球黃金ETF持股月增3%或以上的情況共出現25次，對應黃金價格平均月漲約4%。在這25個月中，有21個月伴隨着美國10年期實際收益率的月度下降，中位數月度降幅約為13個基點，意味聯儲局減息的時機和幅度將直接影響黃金表現。&lt;br/&gt;雖然市場預期聯儲局本周幾乎肯定按兵不動，但摩通指持續疲弱的私人就業增長數據將足以改變市場觀點及確定9月減息，屆時收益率的下降可能獲得更強動力，加速資金輪換進入黃金ETF和期貨市場。在樂觀情況下，金價預計將在年底上試3,675美元的目標價，並預計明年初達到4,000美元。&lt;br/&gt;貿易協定達成壓制金價&lt;br/&gt;然而，隨着美國公佈與日本和菲律賓等國的貿易協定，加上市場傳出歐美貿易協定取得進展，對金價造成壓制，上周未能企穩於3,400美元以上。事實上，金價自5月以來，亦主要在3,200至3,400美元區間震盪。以技術上來看，摩通指金價數月來的盤整走勢在中期前景中保持積極，並消化了超買狀態，關鍵支撐位在3,245美元。&lt;br/&gt;美本周迎3大重要數據&lt;br/&gt;本周經濟數據方面，經濟學家預測周三公佈的美國第二季GDP將受惠於貿易赤字急劇收窄，按年增速有望達2.4%，較首季萎縮0.5%顯著改善。此外，美國周四公佈的6月個人消費支出報告，預計將顯示聯儲局青睞的核心通脹指標環比略有加速，表明關稅僅逐漸轉嫁到消費者身上。至於周五公佈的7月非農報告預計將印證企業招聘趨於謹慎，在6月教育行業就業激增推高數據後，本月新增就業料將放緩，失業率或微升至4.2%。&lt;br/&gt;來源網址 : 金價衝高需ETF資金重燃-大行點出關鍵催化劑-明年目標4000美元 | 星島頭條&lt;br/&gt;&lt;a class="bburl" href="https://www.stheadline.com/investment/3477182/" target="_blank" uhash="347278cfe2e7df030f9e0f1a067f5d5a"&gt;https://www.stheadline.com/investment/3477182/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=31992382&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=11048808076886e0aef05759_14635902"/><published>2025-07-27T21:42:17+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>6dfdffb33fd67b81e28343cff6807426</id><title>商湯發佈日日新V6.5大模型及「悟能」具身智能平台</title><updated>2025-07-27T21:43:41+08:00</updated><author><name>258仔仔</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-07-27T21:43:41+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_573382177"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_573382177"&gt;&lt;span id="attach_16394097" onmouseover="showMenu(this.id, 0, 1)" style="position: absolute; display: none"&gt;&lt;img border="0" src="images/discuss_style/attachimg.gif"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;div class="post-img-container" data-pid="573382177" original-img="https://img.discuss.com.hk/attachments/day_250727/20250727_0074fbd0fe12a697569c18pTNzHOoucF.png"&gt;&lt;img border="0" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/3e0398/f/800x0/https://img.discuss.com.hk/attachments/day_250727/20250727_0074fbd0fe12a697569c18pTNzHOoucF.png"/&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="t_attach" id="attach_16394097_menu" style="position: absolute; display: none"&gt;&lt;img alt="" border="0" class="absmiddle" src="images/attachicons/image.gif"&gt; &lt;a href="attachment.php?aid=16394097&amp;amp;nothumb=yes" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;image.png&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt; (668.46 KB)&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="t_smallfont"&gt;2025-7-27 21:43&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;br/&gt;據內媒報道，商湯（020）在世界人工智能大會（WAIC）一個論壇上正式發布「日日新V6.5大模型」及「悟能」具身智能平台，其中日日新V6.5大模型在推理方面有較大程度升級，隨着多模態性能提升，令成本大幅下降。&lt;br/&gt;為機器人提供強大感知&lt;br/&gt;報道提到，「悟能」具身智能平台以商湯具身世界模型為核心引擎，依託商湯大裝置提供端側和雲側算力支持，能夠為機器人、智能設備提供強大感知、視覺導航及多模態交互能力。商湯具身世界模型還能夠產生多視角視頻，確保時間一致性和空間一致性，讓機器能夠理解、生成、編輯真實世界，在空間層面實現世界交互，並構建面向人、物、場的4D真實世界。&lt;br/&gt;來源網址 : 商湯發佈日日新V65大模型及悟能具身智能平台 | 星島頭條&lt;br/&gt;&lt;a class="bburl" href="https://www.stheadline.com/realtime-finance/3477153/" target="_blank" uhash="bd911929504952b33a3c1f675f8509f8"&gt;https://www.stheadline.com/realtime-finance/3477153/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=31992384&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=11048808076886e0aef05759_14635902"/><published>2025-07-27T21:43:41+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>5a63aac60cbfcfcc77a191ddb8b2f6bc</id><title>特斯拉無人駕駛，切底失敗，沽得⁉️</title><updated>2025-07-27T21:44:18+08:00</updated><author><name>忍不住想偷笑</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-07-27T21:44:18+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_573382186"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_573382186"&gt;&lt;span id="attach_16394098" onmouseover="showMenu(this.id, 0, 1)" style="position: absolute; display: none"&gt;&lt;img border="0" src="images/discuss_style/attachimg.gif"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;div class="post-img-container" data-pid="573382186" original-img="https://img.discuss.com.hk/attachments/day_250727/20250727_4ef5fc025474a23c69f2HPoXT1T328mu.jpg"&gt;&lt;img border="0" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/a0b989/f/800x0/https://img.discuss.com.hk/attachments/day_250727/20250727_4ef5fc025474a23c69f2HPoXT1T328mu.jpg"/&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="t_attach" id="attach_16394098_menu" style="position: absolute; display: none"&gt;&lt;img alt="" border="0" class="absmiddle" src="images/attachicons/image.gif"&gt; &lt;a href="attachment.php?aid=16394098&amp;amp;nothumb=yes" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;FB_IMG_1753623707817.jpg&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt; (129.37 KB)&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="t_smallfont"&gt;2025-7-27 21:44&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=31992386&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=11048808076886e0aef05759_14635902"/><published>2025-07-27T21:44:18+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>b787065de7b846b2385e2272ffc6d2c7</id><title>騰訊首發佈及開源3D世界生成模式 大幅縮短生產周期</title><updated>2025-07-27T21:45:18+08:00</updated><author><name>258仔仔</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-07-27T21:45:18+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_573382201"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_573382201"&gt;&lt;span id="attach_16394109" onmouseover="showMenu(this.id, 0, 1)" style="position: absolute; display: none"&gt;&lt;img border="0" src="images/discuss_style/attachimg.gif"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;div class="post-img-container" data-pid="573382201" original-img="https://img.discuss.com.hk/attachments/day_250727/20250727_74b3afa24ac168646c40Re7KRDySj7rQ.png"&gt;&lt;img border="0" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/a24237/f/800x0/https://img.discuss.com.hk/attachments/day_250727/20250727_74b3afa24ac168646c40Re7KRDySj7rQ.png"/&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="t_attach" id="attach_16394109_menu" style="position: absolute; display: none"&gt;&lt;img alt="" border="0" class="absmiddle" src="images/attachicons/image.gif"&gt; &lt;a href="attachment.php?aid=16394109&amp;amp;nothumb=yes" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;image.png&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt; (462.84 KB)&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="t_smallfont"&gt;2025-7-27 21:45&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;br/&gt;據內媒報道，騰訊（700）旗下騰訊雲副總裁吳運聲今日（27日）在世界人工智能大會（WAIC）一個論壇上，正式發佈及開源業界首個3D世界生成模型「混元3D世界模型1.0」，用戶只需輸入一句話或一張圖，就能夠在幾分鐘之內生成可漫遊的3D世界，大幅縮短生產周期。此外，他透露未來仍有非常多模型即將開源。&lt;br/&gt;推出了一系列開源舉措&lt;br/&gt;另一方面，騰訊混元在其微信公眾號發聲明表示，「混元3D世界模型1.0」是業界首個具備沉浸式漫遊、互動、模擬功能的開源3D世界模型，融合了全景視覺生成和分層3D重建技術。同時，騰訊混元部門也推出了一系列開源舉措，包括設備上混合推理語言模型、多模態理解模型和遊戲視覺模型。&lt;br/&gt;來源網址 : 騰訊首發佈及開源3D世界生成模式-大幅縮短生產周期 | 星島頭條&lt;br/&gt;&lt;a class="bburl" href="https://www.stheadline.com/realtime-finance/3477152/" target="_blank" uhash="1967d9ad03d3d0e9ce67d2ac4abfc8d2"&gt;https://www.stheadline.com/realtime-finance/3477152/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=31992389&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=11048808076886e0aef05759_14635902"/><published>2025-07-27T21:45:18+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>81a12b833f9fa7049356b3d7b12a4404</id><title>百度3大AI技術亮相WAIC 發佈新一代數字人技術NOVA</title><updated>2025-07-27T21:46:30+08:00</updated><author><name>258仔仔</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-07-27T21:46:30+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_573382223"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_573382223"&gt;&lt;span id="attach_16394111" onmouseover="showMenu(this.id, 0, 1)" style="position: absolute; display: none"&gt;&lt;img border="0" src="images/discuss_style/attachimg.gif"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;div class="post-img-container" data-pid="573382223" original-img="https://img.discuss.com.hk/attachments/day_250727/20250727_5327993b43814d23d0cd1vbK4L0Ix2Tq.png"&gt;&lt;img border="0" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/828c66/f/800x0/https://img.discuss.com.hk/attachments/day_250727/20250727_5327993b43814d23d0cd1vbK4L0Ix2Tq.png"/&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="t_attach" id="attach_16394111_menu" style="position: absolute; display: none"&gt;&lt;img alt="" border="0" class="absmiddle" src="images/attachicons/image.gif"&gt; &lt;a href="attachment.php?aid=16394111&amp;amp;nothumb=yes" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;image.png&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt; (1.17 MB)&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="t_smallfont"&gt;2025-7-27 21:46&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;br/&gt;百度（9988）在世界人工智能大會（WAIC）上宣布，百度慧播星發佈新一代數字人技術NOVA，並預計於10月向全行業開放，屆時普通用戶也可獲得媲美頭部主播的專業帶貨能力。此外，百度旗下3大AI核心技術與產品，包括蘿蔔快跑、飛槳深度學習平台及百度智算集群，入選中國人工智能產業創新成果展。據悉，蘿蔔快跑還擔任了本屆WAIC大會接駁車。&lt;br/&gt;NOVA技術已進入邀測階段&lt;br/&gt;百度慧播星表示，以羅永浩數字人為藍本的超頭主播能力復刻進入規模化量產時代，該技術曾支撐羅永浩數字人直播間創下5,500萬GMV。目前NOVA技術已進入邀測階段，提前應用於教育、健康等10多個行業的達人與商家。&lt;br/&gt;根據內媒指出，NOVA依託文心大模型4.5的大師級劇本模式，能生成優質腳本並驅動多模態協同，讓數字人在直播間實現形神音容的高度匹配；搭載的AI大腦可即時接收直播數據並自主決策，調度多智能體完成問答互動，並結合熱點輸出風格化內容；高效復刻能力僅需10分鐘真人樣本，就能完成聲情動作復刻，實現聲音、動作與氛圍的精準匹配。&lt;br/&gt;來源網址 : 百度3大AI技術亮相WAIC-發佈新一代數字人技術NOVA | 星島頭條&lt;br/&gt;&lt;a class="bburl" href="https://www.stheadline.com/realtime-finance/3477092/" target="_blank" uhash="5b667cdad8a23686a88f4ea704ec4982"&gt;https://www.stheadline.com/realtime-finance/3477092/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=31992390&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=11048808076886e0aef05759_14635902"/><published>2025-07-27T21:46:30+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>74509daa6072b9944e50a425cf398bc9</id><title>內地工業企業半年少賺1.8% 裝備製造業增長快 國統局：政策效果續顯</title><updated>2025-07-27T21:47:55+08:00</updated><author><name>258仔仔</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-07-27T21:47:55+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_573382239"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_573382239"&gt;&lt;span id="attach_16394112" onmouseover="showMenu(this.id, 0, 1)" style="position: absolute; display: none"&gt;&lt;img border="0" src="images/discuss_style/attachimg.gif"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;div class="post-img-container" data-pid="573382239" original-img="https://img.discuss.com.hk/attachments/day_250727/20250727_a8719436357be59227a6S2oXrOwm5WQN.png"&gt;&lt;img border="0" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/82d298/f/800x0/https://img.discuss.com.hk/attachments/day_250727/20250727_a8719436357be59227a6S2oXrOwm5WQN.png"/&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="t_attach" id="attach_16394112_menu" style="position: absolute; display: none"&gt;&lt;img alt="" border="0" class="absmiddle" src="images/attachicons/image.gif"&gt; &lt;a href="attachment.php?aid=16394112&amp;amp;nothumb=yes" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;image.png&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt; (475.05 KB)&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="t_smallfont"&gt;2025-7-27 21:47&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;br/&gt;國家統計局公布，1至6月份，全國規模以上工業企業實現利潤總額約3.44萬億元（人民幣，下同），按年跌1.8%。單計6月份，規模以上工業企業利潤按年跌4.3%，跌幅較5月收窄4.8個百分點，其中製造業改善明顯，利潤由5月下降4.1%轉為增長1.4%。&lt;br/&gt;國企利潤按年跌7.6%&lt;br/&gt;今年首6個月，規模以上工業企業中，國有控股企業實現利潤1.1萬億元，按年跌7.6%；股份制企業實現利潤2.53萬億元，按年跌3.1%；外商及港澳台投資企業實現利潤8,823.1億元，增長2.5%；私營企業實現利潤9,389.7億元，增長1.7%。&lt;br/&gt;期內，採礦業利潤4,294.1億元，按年跌30.3%；製造業利潤總額2.59萬億元，增長4.5%；電力、熱力、燃氣及水生産和供應業利潤4,170.4億元，增長3.3%。&lt;br/&gt;黑色金屬冶煉業多賺13.7倍&lt;br/&gt;細分行業之中，黑色金屬冶煉和壓延加工業利潤按年增長13.7倍；農副食品加工業增長22.8%；電氣機械和器材製造業增長13%；有色金屬冶煉及壓延加工業增長7.8% ；通用設備製造業增長6.5%；電力、熱力生產和供應業增長5.6%；專用設備製造業增長4.4%；汽車製造業增長3.6%；而計算機、通信和其他電子設備製造業則增長3.5%。&lt;br/&gt;相反，非金屬礦物製品業下降5.4%；紡織業下降8.1%；化學原料和化學制品製造業下降9%；石油和天然氣開採業下降11.5%；煤炭開採和洗選業下降53%；石油、煤炭及其他燃料加工業按年虧損增加。&lt;br/&gt;「高端化、智慧化、綠色化深入推進」&lt;br/&gt;國統局工業司統計師于衞寧表示，6月規模以上工業企業利潤按年降幅較5月有所收窄，以裝備工業為代表的新動能行業利潤增長較快，企業效益狀況呈現幾項特點，包括「營業收入維持增長，企業利潤降幅收窄」、「裝備製造業營收、利潤快速增長」、「製造業高端化、智慧化、綠色化深入推進」，以及「兩新政策帶動效果持續顯現」，下階段面對複雜多變的外部環境，要做大做強國內大循環，堅定不移推動工業經濟高品質發展，不斷鞏固工業企業效益恢復基礎。&lt;br/&gt;來源網址 : 內地工業企業半年少賺18-裝備製造業增長快-國統局政策效果續顯 | 星島頭條&lt;br/&gt;&lt;a class="bburl" href="https://www.stheadline.com/macroeconomics/3477119/" target="_blank" uhash="b1dddf9722d09cede235f1ff039ef6f6"&gt;https://www.stheadline.com/macroeconomics/3477119/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=31992392&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=11048808076886e0aef05759_14635902"/><published>2025-07-27T21:47:55+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>dcb41bb474e1e268dad9d28f4d933706</id><title>雞佬侵要製造業重返美國根本不可能！（含AI分析）</title><updated>2025-07-27T22:27:30+08:00</updated><author><name>太監豬王係騙徒</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-07-27T22:27:30+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_573382656"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_573382656"&gt;The rise in obesity rates in the U.S. and Britain, the challenges this poses for the manufacturing sector, and the feasibility of Trump’s push to bring manufacturing back to America. Here’s a breakdown of the key points:&lt;br&gt;---&lt;br/&gt;### 1. **Rising Obesity Rates in the U.S. and Britain**&lt;br/&gt; - **Historical Trends**: In the U.S., obesity rates have tripled since the 1960s, with nearly 70% of adults now classified as overweight or obese. Severe obesity has increased tenfold . Similar trends are observed in Britain, though specific data isn’t provided in the search results.&lt;br/&gt; - **Causes**: Factors include changes in diet (e.g., increased fast food consumption), sedentary lifestyles, and socioeconomic disparities. For example, lower-income groups in the U.S. often face higher obesity rates due to limited access to healthy food and healthcare .&lt;br/&gt;---&lt;br/&gt;### 2. **Obesity and Manufacturing Workforce Challenges**&lt;br/&gt; - **Physical Demands**: Manufacturing jobs often require physical stamina, dexterity, and long hours. As noted in the search results, Chinese workers are highlighted for their work ethic, physical speed, and ability to perform repetitive tasks efficiently—attributes that may be harder to find in a workforce with higher obesity rates .&lt;br/&gt; - **Health and Productivity**: Obesity is linked to higher absenteeism, lower productivity, and increased healthcare costs. For instance, obesity-related medical care costs the U.S. healthcare system $173 billion annually . These factors could make American workers less competitive in labor-intensive manufacturing roles.&lt;br/&gt;---&lt;br/&gt;### 3. **Trump’s Manufacturing Push: Is It Realistic?**&lt;br/&gt; - **Tariffs and Their Limitations**: Trump’s plan relies heavily on tariffs (e.g., 10–49% on imports) to incentivize domestic production. However, experts argue that tariffs alone won’t address deeper issues like supply chain gaps, lack of skilled labor, and high U.S. production costs .&lt;br/&gt; - **Automation Over Labor**: Modern manufacturing increasingly relies on automation, reducing the need for large human workforces. Even if jobs return, they may require advanced technical skills rather than manual labor, which doesn’t necessarily align with the current workforce’s capabilities .&lt;br/&gt; - **Cultural and Infrastructure Barriers**: The U.S. lacks the industrial supply chains (e.g., component factories) and worker training programs needed to compete with countries like China. For example, Apple’s CEO noted the U.S. lacks enough tooling engineers to fill a room, while China could fill football fields .&lt;br/&gt;---&lt;br/&gt;### 4. **Conclusion: Is Trump’s Plan Unrealistic?**&lt;br/&gt; - **Yes, but Not Just Due to Obesity**: While rising obesity rates may exacerbate workforce challenges, they are just one of many barriers. The larger issues include:&lt;br/&gt; 1. **High Costs**: U.S. labor and infrastructure costs make domestic production uncompetitive .&lt;br/&gt; 2. **Skill Gaps**: The workforce isn’t trained for modern manufacturing roles .&lt;br/&gt; 3. **Global Supply Chains**: Rebuilding them domestically would take decades .&lt;br/&gt; - **Obesity as a Symptom**: The obesity epidemic reflects broader societal and economic trends (e.g., food systems, healthcare access) that tariffs cannot fix. Addressing manufacturing decline requires holistic solutions, including education reform, infrastructure investment, and healthcare improvements .&lt;br/&gt;---&lt;br/&gt;### Final Answer:&lt;br/&gt;Trump’s push to bring manufacturing back to America faces significant hurdles, including obesity-related workforce challenges, but the larger barriers are economic and structural. Tariffs alone cannot overcome the high costs, skill gaps, and supply chain deficiencies that make U.S. manufacturing uncompetitive. While obesity may reduce the pool of physically capable workers, the plan’s unrealistic assumptions about labor, automation, and global trade dynamics are the primary reasons it’s unlikely to succeed .&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=31992422&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=11048808076886e0aef05759_14635902"/><published>2025-07-27T22:27:30+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>6436b8588f38b3ca920863325d05ad66</id><title>週末ig升156</title><updated>2025-07-28T00:16:09+08:00</updated><author><name>樣衰長臭蟹</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-07-28T00:16:09+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_573383812"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_573383812"&gt;殺熊&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=31992508&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=11048808076886e0aef05759_14635902"/><published>2025-07-28T00:16:09+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>fc1905aee4bc58766cb9a7b831b208ac</id><title>🫵🚬🐸估到契弟21哥：可能秘密炒牛熊想好似呢位仁兄咁叻…同樣用500,000炒上3,240,000</title><updated>2025-07-28T05:29:08+08:00</updated><author><name>破馬會操盤強人</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-07-28T05:29:08+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_573384857"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_573384857"&gt;&lt;span id="attach_16394725" onmouseover="showMenu(this.id, 0, 1)" style="position: absolute; display: none"&gt;&lt;img border="0" src="images/discuss_style/attachimg.gif"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;div class="post-img-container" data-pid="573384857" original-img="https://img.discuss.com.hk/attachments/day_250728/20250728_73c34991bdb5a801cc79H0ov1shFXs0t.jpg"&gt;&lt;img border="0" src="https://cdn.dis